This projects runs in docker container, managed with docker-compose

You must run `rspec` in the api container, use the following command. Use any options and argument you need
```
lago exec api bundle exec rspec
```

You must just the `rails` cli in the container (to use `db:migrate` or `generate` for instance)
```
lago exec api bin/rails
```
